billy : the early years is a 2008 american biographical film directed by robby benson . the film tells the story of the early life of evangelist billy graham , played by armie hammer . world wide pictures , the film distribution and production company that was created by the billy graham &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; association ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) , did not work on the film 's production . after almost a year and a half of delays , the film was released on dvd on march 16 , 2010 .